      * ADD  PROTRUST A09,A20                       *
JW1   * ADD  D3@ FOR AR8133                         *
%0001 * ADD  JB@ FOR JL BLUE         T.SAKAKI       *
JW2   * ADD  PASS 20180618 (EFFECTIVE DATE)         *
%0002 * ADD  TABLE FILE INSTEAD OF SCD              *
     F***********************************************
     FAJHPL01 UP  E           K        DISK
     FAAHTL06 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFCGPL51 IF  E           K        DISK
